    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Publish short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive end to end\n\n**Pattern:** Video Production · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nPublish short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive end to end. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual publishing is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse XLSX Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Google Sheets → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to video production without manual effort\n- Anyone automating publishing in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
